      "rationale": "The FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) is a commercially validated code with documented SQA procedures. All analysis scripts are version-controlled under a 21 CFR Part 11-compliant repository. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for a medium model risk COU."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
